  "description": "A mechanic is a discrete system within a game's [rules](./rules.md) that governs how a specific kind of action or interaction works. Drawing cards is a mechanic. Rolling dice to resolve uncertainty is a mechanic. Bidding, auctioning, drafting, tile placement, and resource trading are all mechanics.",
